/*
    HOURS COUNT v2

    It's se 2nd version of the 1st script
    It's supposed to be faster in comparison of the v1

    Data are extracted from (REPARTITION_PERSONNEL_STJO_SERVICE_ACM_2019-2020) in the RECAP tab
